{"id": "1398745302998974497", "channel_id": "1398745302998974497", "type": 0, "author_id": "352428907468947474", "author_name": "sophiechoice", "author_bot": false, "content": "There are a few skills that you simply can't upgrade on PC, because it forces a tooltip with the skill description to open, but doesn't let you select the card to upgrade. You can click away from the tooltip to make it disappear, but then trying to select the card you want to level will once again make the tooltip appear and lock you out of upgrading it.", "timestamp": "2025-07-26T19:14:27.666000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1398745304081371217", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1304143, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1398745302998974497/1398745304081371217/image.png?ex=69cc1d13&is=69cacb93&hm=110acb186374d68ee3480de57ca59df6a15cbfee6d491d4178e2803d612dd9e2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1398745302998974497", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」Impossible to upgrade certain skills on the PC client!", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
